Key to the Ethiopian species of 
<taxonomicName id="89FC54F1FFE9FF88FD43FE5CF31F97F9" authorityName="Friese" authorityYear="1903" box="[656,801,484,510]" class="Insecta" family="Andrenidae" genus="Meliturgula" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
